      • signWith

        public Transaction signWith(PublicKey publicKey,
                            TransactionSigner signer)
        Sign the transaction with a callback that may block waiting for user confirmation.
        Parameters:
        publicKey - the public key that pairs with the signature. Currently only Ed25519PublicKey is allowed.
        signer - the labmda to generate the signature.
        Returns:
        this for fluent usage.
        See Also:
        TransactionSigner

      • hash

        public byte[] hash()
        Calculate the expected hash of the transaction. The transaction must have all required signatures and have the node account id set in order to be accurate.
        Returns:
        the expected hash of the transaction
